{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "ikido-dev-tasks-reset",
		"name": "iKidO - Dev Tasks Reset",
		"description": "Development-only collection for resetting the tasks module.\n\n⚠️ **WARNING**: These endpoints are ONLY available in development mode.\n\n## Setup\n\n1. Create a Postman environment variable:\n   - Variable: `dev_admin_key`\n   - Value: Your `DEV_ADMIN_KEY` from `.env.local`\n\n2. Set the `base_url` variable:\n   - Variable: `base_url`\n   - Value: `http://localhost:3000` (or your dev server URL)\n\n## Usage\n\nRun the request to reset:\n- All child_task assignments\n- All children's points_balance to 0\n- All ggpoints_ledger entries\n- All custom tasks (preserves global tasks)",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "Reset Tasks Module",
			"event": [
				{
					"listen": "test",
					"script": {
						"exec": [
							"// Test response structure",
							"pm.test(\"Status code is 200\", function () {",
							"    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
							"});",
							"",
							"pm.test(\"Response has success field\", function () {",
							"    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
							"    pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property('success');",
							"    pm.expect(jsonData.success).to.be.true;",
							"});",
							"",
							"pm.test(\"Response has deleted counts\", function () {",
							"    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
							"    pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property('deleted_child_tasks');",
							"    pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property('deleted_ledger_entries');",
							"    pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property('deleted_custom_tasks');",
							"    pm.expect(jsonData).to.have.property('cleared_points');",
							"});",
							"",
							"// Log response for debugging",
							"console.log(\"Reset completed:\", pm.response.json());"
						],
						"type": "text/javascript"
					}
				},
				{
					"listen": "prerequest",
					"script": {
						"exec": [
							"// Validate required environment variables",
							"if (!pm.environment.get('dev_admin_key')) {",
							"    console.warn('⚠️ Warning: dev_admin_key not set in environment');",
							"    console.warn('Please set dev_admin_key in your Postman environment');",
							"}",
							"",
							"if (!pm.environment.get('base_url')) {",
							"    console.warn('⚠️ Warning: base_url not set, using default');",
							"    pm.environment.set('base_url', 'http://localhost:3000');",
							"}"
						],
						"type": "text/javascript"
					}
				}
			],
			"request": {
				"method": "POST",
				"header": [
					{
						"key": "Content-Type",
						"value": "application/json",
						"type": "text"
					},
					{
						"key": "x-admin-key",
						"value": "{{dev_admin_key}}",
						"type": "text",
						"description": "Admin key from DEV_ADMIN_KEY environment variable"
					}
				],
				"body": {
					"mode": "raw",
					"raw": "{}",
					"options": {
						"raw": {
							"language": "json"
						}
					}
				},
				"url": {
					"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/dev/tasks/reset",
					"host": [
						"{{base_url}}"
					],
					"path": [
						"api",
						"dev",
						"tasks",
						"reset"
					]
				},
				"description": "Resets the entire tasks module for development testing.\n\n**Operations performed:**\n1. Delete all child_task assignments\n2. Reset all children's points_balance to 0\n3. Clear all ggpoints_ledger entries\n4. Delete all custom tasks (is_global = false)\n5. Preserve global tasks (is_global = true)\n\n**Security:**\n- Only works in development mode (NODE_ENV !== 'production')\n- Requires x-admin-key header with valid DEV_ADMIN_KEY\n\n**Expected Response (200 OK):**\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"Tasks, child assignments, and GGPoints have been fully reset for development testing.\",\n  \"deleted_child_tasks\": 15,\n  \"cleared_points\": true,\n  \"deleted_ledger_entries\": 23,\n  \"deleted_custom_tasks\": 5\n}\n```\n\n**Error Responses:**\n- **403 FORBIDDEN**: Endpoint accessed in production\n- **401 UNAUTHORIZED**: Missing or invalid admin key"
			},
